data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Looking for a spacious home with ample bedrooms and baths? Explore this inviting Adams home featuring 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, complete with a versatile den that can easily serve as an additional bedroom or a convenient home office. Nestled on a corner lot within a peaceful cul-de-sac, this property offers privacy and tranquility.    Indulge in luxury with his and her bathrooms in the primary bedroom, each equipped with separate walk-in closets for added convenience. Recent updates include new bedroom carpets, freshly painted walls, and modern replacements such as the 4-year-young roof and 15 seer A/C. Notably, the hot water heater has been replaced this month, ensuring efficiency and reliability.    The 2-car garage boasts a practical workbench, catering to DIY enthusiasts. Step outside to discover a sprawling yard, a paradise for avid gardeners, where you can simply stroll out and harvest fruits from your very own fruit trees. The property is accompanied by a fully-equipped green house featuring electric, water, and mist systems, perfect for cultivating your favorite plants year-round.    Experience self-sufficiency with a dedicated well and irrigation system, offering resourceful water management. Embrace cozy winter nights by the wood-burning fireplace, adding warmth and charm to the living space. The home's security system includes 8+ cameras, requiring no additional service for operation, ensuring your peace of mind.    Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity. Schedule your appointment today to view this remarkable home that seamlessly combines comfort, functionality, and modern amenities. Owner says don't be afraid to make an offer. Schedule your appointments today.
